Description: Bare-metal mail server suite with guided setup
 KTC Mail provides a non-containerized mail server control plane for
 Debian and Ubuntu. It launches an initial web GUI, prepares DNS and TLS
 automation, and monitors the firewall policy used by the mail stack.
